org.dkpro.core.decompounding.splitter

Class Fragment

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dkpro.core.decompounding.splitter.Fragment

  • public class Fragment
extends Object
    Data container for a split element. A split element contains a word and optional a linking morpheme

    • Constructor Summary

      Creates a split element with a word and a linking morpheme.
